description:
The Purpose of the Organization shall be:

i.	To serve as a connection between current industry professionals and agricultural students.
ii.	To Interact with legislators at both the State level in Albany and the national level in Washington, D.C.;
iii.	To promote agriculture and related fields;
iv.	To offer opportunities for students in leadership and citizenship engagement encompassing career development, service learning and professional networking;
v.	To familiarize members with, and to maintain cooperative relations with, NYFB and AFBF organizations; and 
vi.	To create a diverse student organization that is educated, passionate and up to date on agricultural industry, policy and innovation.
